## IMPORTANT: Difference Between Actions

| Action | Behavior | Speed | Use Case |
|--------|----------|-------|----------|
| **Block** | Drop packets silently | Slow (timeout) | Stealth mode |
| **Reject** | Send "connection refused" | Fast | Better UX |
| **Allow** | Permit traffic | N/A | Whitelist rules |

