## Summary Table: TP4 vs TP5 vs TP6

| Feature | TP4 | TP5 | TP6 |
|---------|-----|-----|-----|
| **Type** | Host-based | Network-based | Network-based |
| **Target** | Individual machine | All network traffic | Specific port/protocol |
| **Blocking** | By program/port | By domain/IP | By port number |
| **Tool** | Windows Firewall | pfSense | pfSense |
| **Scope** | Local computer | Entire LAN | Entire LAN |
| **Granularity** | Per-application | Per-IP/domain | Per-port |
| **Advanced** | Outbound rules | Aliases, NAT | Time-based schedules |

